# PendoMind Cursor Rules

## Required Context

Before starting any task, always read:

1. `CLAUDE.md` - Contains project architecture, commands, and testing patterns
2. `README.md` - Contains usage guide, MCP tools, and quality control info

## Project Guidelines

- Use the pyenv virtual environment: `~/.pyenv/versions/3.12.2/envs/pendomind`
- Run tests with: `~/.pyenv/versions/3.12.2/envs/pendomind/bin/pytest tests/ -v`
- This is a FastMCP server with Qdrant vector database
- All tests mock external dependencies (see `tests/conftest.py`)
